nodes.text: Unidentified Sheathipede-class transport shuttle (Cad Bane's frigate)

A Sheathipede-class transport shuttle was docked aboard Cad Bane's Munificent-class star frigate. It was stolen by Anakin Skywalker, Ahsoka Tano, and Rex when they escaped from Bane's frigate. However, Bane faked his death and was able to escape aboard the shuttle by disguising himself as the clone trooper Denal, who he had killed.
